    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "If you consider GPR as an independent library, then it doesn't really make sense to be able to build it in such a way that it exports do-nothing synchronization functions. It makes more sense to build gRPC so that it simply doesn't use those synchronization functions.\n"
